579
00:34:59,800 --> 00:35:00,640
Uh...

580
00:35:00,880 --> 00:35:01,880
reward?

581
00:35:02,470 --> 00:35:03,360
Your Highness,

582
00:35:03,800 --> 00:35:06,760
