583
00:35:07,030 --> 00:35:08,280
One can dream.

584
00:35:09,630 --> 00:35:10,920
Have you never had dreams?

585
00:35:13,150 --> 00:35:14,070
To be honest,

586
00:35:14,590 --> 00:35:16,920
I thought to myself in private

587
00:35:17,510 --> 00:35:19,920
that if I won by luck,

588
00:35:22,590 --> 00:35:25,960
I'd ask His Majesty for a Pardon Token.

589
00:35:30,510 --> 00:35:31,760
Don't be silly!

590
00:35:33,840 --> 00:35:36,840
A Pardon Token can only save you once.

591
00:35:36,960 --> 00:35:37,800
If

592
00:35:37,800 --> 00:35:40,150
someone keeps setting you up,

593
00:35:40,990 --> 00:35:42,400
that token will be useless.

594
00:35:42,470 --> 00:35:44,240
It can't save you forever.

595
00:35:44,240 --> 00:35:45,440
You'll be killed eventually.

596
00:35:45,880 --> 00:35:46,840
Such things have never

597
00:35:46,840 --> 00:35:48,400
stopped throughout history.

598
00:35:48,400 --> 00:35:49,630
As a member of royalty,

599
00:35:50,190 --> 00:35:52,030
I've seen enough of them.

600
00:35:52,630 --> 00:35:53,470
So

601
00:35:53,720 --> 00:35:55,510
