602
00:35:56,280 --> 00:35:57,280
What you need

603
00:35:57,470 --> 00:35:58,840
isn't a Pardon Token

604
00:35:58,960 --> 00:35:59,800
but status.

605
00:36:01,590 --> 00:36:02,440
Think about it.

606
00:36:03,320 --> 00:36:04,280
With a high status,

607
00:36:04,400 --> 00:36:05,550
you'll gain connections.

608
00:36:05,880 --> 00:36:06,880
With connections,

609
00:36:06,880 --> 00:36:09,760
you'll know more members of the nobility.

610
00:36:10,150 --> 00:36:11,550
When you're in trouble,

611
00:36:11,840 --> 00:36:12,960
only those people

612
00:36:12,960 --> 00:36:15,030
can save your life.

613
00:36:18,280 --> 00:36:19,800
If,

614
00:36:22,360 --> 00:36:23,960
I mean if

615
00:36:25,470 --> 00:36:30,150
you get to know royalty,

616
00:36:30,550 --> 00:36:33,320
and if some blind noble girl

617
00:36:33,320 --> 00:36:34,720
falls for you...

618
00:36:45,960 --> 00:36:47,070
What I'm saying is

619
00:36:47,440 --> 00:36:49,070
if you become one of the imperial family,

620
00:36:49,070 --> 00:36:50,920
no one can threaten you.

621
00:36:51,400 --> 00:36:53,550
You'll enjoy all the glory and wealth

622
00:36:54,110 --> 00:36:55,990
and the masses' respect.

623
00:36:57,190 --> 00:36:58,400
In a word,

624
00:36:58,920 --> 00:37:01,440
a noble status can be of great help,

625
00:37:03,110 --> 00:37:04,400
such as a rank of nobility.

626
00:37:05,030 --> 00:37:05,920
Do you understand?

627
00:37:06,440 --> 00:37:07,280
I do.

628
00:37:08,470 --> 00:37:09,960
I appreciate your advice

629
00:37:10,110 --> 00:37:11,440
and thoughtfulness.

630
00:37:12,240 --> 00:37:13,360
