655
00:38:36,960 --> 00:38:38,470
The duel between the two sides

656
00:38:38,470 --> 00:38:40,110
will begin in three days

657
00:38:40,110 --> 00:38:41,510
in the square of the Star Tower.

658
00:38:41,510 --> 00:38:42,350
Civilians are

659
00:38:42,400 --> 00:38:44,840
