666
00:38:54,110 --> 00:38:56,550
Silver Gong Xu Qi'an will battle the Dharma!

667
00:38:56,990 --> 00:38:58,320
It'll be grand.

668
00:38:58,320 --> 00:39:00,030
Let's go and watch it together.

669
00:39:00,030 --> 00:39:01,670
Yes, we'll all go.

670
00:39:01,850 --> 00:39:02,800
See you in three days.

671
